message: #13274 Football (soccer) died today. Fuck Real, fuck the ref. I feel so sorry for Buffon ;(
#13275 Be brave. Protest during commencement instead of bitching online.

#13267 I don’t believe in God but I hate him, because I’d rather do that than hate my mom. My mom is awesome, but religion made her make some bad choices. I look back now and I’ve forgiven her for her mistakes, but the fact is I’m still too scared to talk to her. I know religion can bring people together, but it can also drive them apart, like with me. The one relationship I’ve always wanted I can’t have because of some old-ass book. Fuck you Jesus.
